description: Old-School Developers Portfolio - Static HTML website hosted on Python SimpleHTTP server. Single-page portfolio application with information about John and Peter, their projects (NAS and Modernizer 200), and a contact form. All content is served from root (/) with no backend endpoints.
notes: Simple static portfolio website running on Python's built-in SimpleHTTP server. No API endpoints discovered. No authentication required. Form submissions are client-side only (preventDefault pattern). Server returns 501 for POST/OPTIONS methods.
